Knowledge sharing empowers - it increases opportunities and health, and helps intelligent choices to be made.

Knowledge sharing is enabled by:
* [[Open licenses]]
* Effective communication. This involves communication skills (developed through some combination of [[education]], practice and commitment), [[communication tools]], and [[bottom-up development]]. [[Empowerment]] also enables better communication, creating a feedback loop, or virtuous cycle. 

See especially:
* [[Knowledge sharing in practice]]
* [[Km4dev]], a common shorthand for "knowledge management for [[international development|(international) development]]"

